{"title":"迎彩车","authors":["余光烈"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎彩车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部　余光烈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举毛主席语录牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面面红旗迎风摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声如雷锣鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜迎彩车来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜迎彩车来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军营变成欢乐的海；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩车满载革命的宝呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金书四卷放光彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双双笑眼泪光闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张张笑脸鲜花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作手中捧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日照心怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日照心怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心飞向中南海；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千歌万曲唱不尽呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声飘到云天外："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们对您无限忠诚无限崇拜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的话咱句句都听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想要一代传一代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们对您无限信仰无限热爱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的书我们字字细读，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永做完全彻底革命派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是我们最英明的舵手和统帅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士要一辈子读您的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定让毛泽东思想照红全世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗红心都在跳啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动的热泪挂满腮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想哺育咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士长成栋梁材。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}